00:00:14.076 --> 00:00:16.716 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Why did I want to direct
a WWDC opening number?

00:00:18.076 --> 00:00:18.946 A:middle
Good question.

00:00:19.546 --> 00:00:21.566 A:middle
You know, I think I've always
been attracted to risk.

00:00:21.916 --> 00:00:26.386 A:middle
You know? When I shared my
vision for the number, I --

00:00:26.386 --> 00:00:30.796 A:middle
you know, they said this is
just a developers conference.

00:00:30.926 --> 00:00:32.816 A:middle
You know? You don't
need to overthink it.

00:00:33.526 --> 00:00:37.896 A:middle
But I always feel that my job as
a director is to push an idea.

00:00:38.736 --> 00:00:39.156 A:middle
What's that?

00:00:39.676 --> 00:00:40.406 A:middle
Am I a genius?

00:00:40.626 --> 00:00:41.146 A:middle
I don't know.

00:00:41.246 --> 00:00:41.416 A:middle
What!

00:00:41.886 --> 00:00:42.246 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Hey, David.

00:00:42.246 --> 00:00:43.096 A:middle
Are you ready for
the walkthrough?

00:00:43.586 --> 00:00:43.676 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:00:44.596 --> 00:00:46.336 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Who are you talking
to in here?

00:00:47.146 --> 00:00:47.466 A:middle
&gt;&gt; No one.

00:00:47.666 --> 00:00:49.106 A:middle
&gt;&gt; You were talking to somebody.

00:00:49.166 --> 00:00:51.006 A:middle
Unless you were talking
to yourself.

00:00:51.006 --> 00:00:53.406 A:middle
&gt;&gt; I have been working on this
new app called Work Crush.

00:00:53.536 --> 00:00:55.806 A:middle
It's for people who have crushes
on their workmates and want

00:00:55.806 --> 00:00:57.156 A:middle
to know when they are nearby.

00:00:57.766 --> 00:01:01.416 A:middle
It's not for me, but
-- oh, oh, hi, David.

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:57.766 --> 00:01:01.416 A:middle
It's not for me, but
-- oh, oh, hi, David.

00:01:01.416 --> 00:01:02.936 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Yeah, I thought you were
supposed to be guarding my door.

00:01:02.936 --> 00:01:03.846 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Which one is your door?

00:01:04.736 --> 00:01:06.346 A:middle
&gt;&gt; This is Rick.

00:01:06.576 --> 00:01:07.116 A:middle
Rick, look at me.

00:01:07.576 --> 00:01:08.506 A:middle
I need you angry in there, Rick.

00:01:08.616 --> 00:01:10.686 A:middle
I need you angry, angry, angry!

00:01:11.466 --> 00:01:11.546 A:middle
Yeah!

00:01:12.396 --> 00:01:14.066 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Did you get that email
about my email not working?

00:01:14.236 --> 00:01:14.546 A:middle
&gt;&gt; No.

00:01:14.546 --> 00:01:15.546 A:middle
&gt;&gt; What? No, no, no.

00:01:15.546 --> 00:01:18.166 A:middle
It needs to be more
like, you know, Pshhhh!

00:01:18.536 --> 00:01:20.286 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Yeah, he means bigger.

00:01:20.286 --> 00:01:21.946 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Bigger, bigger, yeah,
like developers are on fire!

00:01:22.356 --> 00:01:23.026 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Which iPhone do you want

00:01:23.026 --> 00:01:23.976 A:middle
for the main character,
silver or gold?

00:01:24.086 --> 00:01:25.016 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Can I see silver?

00:01:25.016 --> 00:01:25.956 A:middle
Okay. Can I see gold?

00:01:26.216 --> 00:01:26.446 A:middle
Okay.

00:01:30.226 --> 00:01:31.946 A:middle
I can't tell because
the reflection

00:01:31.946 --> 00:01:32.806 A:middle
of the flame is on it.

00:01:32.806 --> 00:01:34.176 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Can you decide this later?

00:01:36.276 --> 00:01:37.506 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Yeah, he is right.

00:01:37.506 --> 00:01:38.046 A:middle
Let's decide it later.

00:01:38.046 --> 00:01:39.346 A:middle
&gt;&gt; We'll take the gold.

00:01:41.046 --> 00:01:42.726 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Got to choose a talent
for the dating app number.

00:01:42.956 --> 00:01:44.746 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Yes. No.

00:01:45.016 --> 00:01:46.736 A:middle
Yes. No. Yeah.

00:01:47.236 --> 00:01:48.366 A:middle
The pretty one.

00:01:48.366 --> 00:01:48.826 A:middle
&gt;&gt; That's you.

00:01:49.056 --> 00:01:50.626 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Whoa! Did you do that?

00:01:50.986 --> 00:01:51.406 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Yes.

00:01:52.066 --> 00:01:52.496 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Oh, my gosh!

00:01:52.746 --> 00:01:53.856 A:middle
That's my coffee.

00:01:54.306 --> 00:01:54.386 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:01:55.776 --> 00:01:56.386 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Ahhh! Oh, cool.

00:01:57.366 --> 00:01:58.616 A:middle
Oh, that's awesome.

00:01:58.616 --> 00:01:59.456 A:middle
Did you bring my sugar?

