&gt;&gt; David, what have
you got me into here?

00:02:33.976 --> 00:02:35.456 A:middle
Am I like a Victoria's
Secret guy?

00:02:35.546 --> 00:02:36.916 A:middle
&gt;&gt; You are an angel investor.

00:02:36.916 --> 00:02:39.766 A:middle
You make millions
off kids' dreams.

00:02:40.076 --> 00:02:41.236 A:middle
&gt;&gt; So I am just a rich guy?

00:02:41.236 --> 00:02:42.126 A:middle
&gt;&gt; You are a rich guy.

00:02:42.626 --> 00:02:44.516 A:middle
Bring him up.

00:02:45.146 --> 00:02:46.976 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Ooh, this harness cuts the
circulation off in my legs.

00:02:47.046 --> 00:02:48.776 A:middle
&gt;&gt; That's all right, buddy.

00:02:48.776 --> 00:02:48.956 A:middle
No worries.

00:02:55.846 --> 00:02:56.596 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Let's run it.

00:02:56.596 --> 00:02:58.716 A:middle
&gt;&gt; No, I say when we run it.

00:02:58.866 --> 00:02:59.146 A:middle
Who is it?

00:02:59.186 --> 00:02:59.926 A:middle
Why is he saying my words?

