&gt;&gt; Run it.

00:03:04.136 --> 00:03:04.676 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Thank you.

00:03:07.346 --> 00:03:11.916 A:middle
&gt;&gt; So many days of dev time,
haven't seen a ray of sunshine.

00:03:12.046 --> 00:03:14.196 A:middle
Locked in my coding lair.

00:03:14.196 --> 00:03:17.976 A:middle
It's been days since I
changed my underwear.

00:03:18.246 --> 00:03:19.896 A:middle
My app is in the Store?

00:03:20.366 --> 00:03:21.976 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Your app is in the Store.

00:03:22.066 --> 00:03:24.006 A:middle
&gt;&gt; From the whiteboard
to the App Store

00:03:24.006 --> 00:03:25.886 A:middle
because when I code,
I'm swift, boy.

00:03:26.096 --> 00:03:28.976 A:middle
Yeah, I rule Objective-C,
objective one, objective me.

00:03:29.076 --> 00:03:30.016 A:middle
See the app, I made that.

00:03:30.116 --> 00:03:30.976 A:middle
Download my game, you play that.

00:03:31.046 --> 00:03:33.146 A:middle
App of the day, now
I'm worldwide.

00:03:33.366 --> 00:03:34.596 A:middle
Five stars, now watch me shine.

00:03:35.416 --> 00:03:36.346 A:middle
You made the cut.

00:03:36.686 --> 00:03:37.466 A:middle
The world is yours.

00:03:38.046 --> 00:03:40.846 A:middle
Now that your app
is in the Store.

00:03:41.396 --> 00:03:43.736 A:middle
This is your break,
your time to fly.

00:03:44.146 --> 00:03:47.586 A:middle
So raise your hands
up and touch the sky.

00:03:56.156 --> 00:03:56.446 A:middle
&gt;&gt; What happened?

00:03:56.536 --> 00:03:57.956 A:middle
&gt;&gt; The generator's blown.

00:03:58.106 --> 00:03:58.296 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Dammit!

00:03:58.496 --> 00:04:00.936 A:middle
Can I at least get a work light?

WEBVTT
