Good morning!

00:05:01.486 --> 00:05:05.136 A:middle
Thanks for joining us.

00:05:06.046 --> 00:05:07.726 A:middle
And welcome to San Francisco.

00:05:07.726 --> 00:05:11.096 A:middle
Welcome to WWDC 2015.

00:05:11.706 --> 00:05:14.376 A:middle
Although we may not
have any -- thank you --

00:05:14.786 --> 00:05:18.596 A:middle
high-flying trapeze acts, we
do have a lot of great things

00:05:18.596 --> 00:05:19.856 A:middle
to talk about this morning.

00:05:20.596 --> 00:05:23.906 A:middle
This developer conference
continues to be the epicenter

00:05:23.906 --> 00:05:27.786 A:middle
of change for not only
Apple, but the industry.

00:05:28.976 --> 00:05:32.346 A:middle
This is our 26th WWDC.

00:05:32.346 --> 00:05:35.576 A:middle
We have attendees today
from over 70 countries,

00:05:35.956 --> 00:05:38.766 A:middle
and 80 percent are here
for the very first time.

00:05:39.516 --> 00:05:44.566 A:middle
[Applause]

