started with OS X.

00:08:39.275 --> 00:08:40.956 A:middle
We are bringing a whole bunch

00:08:40.956 --> 00:08:43.456 A:middle
of new great capabilities
to the Macintosh.

00:08:44.236 --> 00:08:47.476 A:middle
And next we've got a
great update for iOS,

00:08:48.056 --> 00:08:50.696 A:middle
the world's most advanced
mobile operating system.

00:08:51.446 --> 00:08:55.196 A:middle
And today we're bringing
native apps

00:08:55.746 --> 00:08:57.976 A:middle
to the Watch with a new version.

00:08:58.516 --> 00:09:02.636 A:middle
[Applause]

