In fact, over 55 percent

00:10:33.846 --> 00:10:36.316 A:middle
of active Mac users are
running our latest update,

00:10:36.656 --> 00:10:40.276 A:middle
and this is just unprecedented
in the history of our industry.

00:10:41.096 --> 00:10:45.716 A:middle
[Laughter] In fact, Yosemite
has the fastest adoption rate

00:10:45.766 --> 00:10:48.086 A:middle
for any PC operating
system ever.

00:10:48.086 --> 00:10:48.956 A:middle
So thank you.

00:10:49.516 --> 00:10:55.476 A:middle
[Applause]

00:10:55.976 --> 00:10:59.696 A:middle
So for our next big release of
OS X, we knew we wanted to build

00:10:59.696 --> 00:11:01.616 A:middle
on those strengths of Yosemite

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:10:59.696 --> 00:11:01.616 A:middle
on those strengths of Yosemite

00:11:01.976 --> 00:11:04.656 A:middle
with some really great
refinements and advances.

00:11:05.176 --> 00:11:08.386 A:middle
The only real question, of
course, was what to call it.

00:11:09.616 --> 00:11:13.836 A:middle
So we had to once again turn to
our crack Apple Marketing Team.

00:11:15.466 --> 00:11:19.096 A:middle
Now, in typical California
fashion, they started

00:11:19.166 --> 00:11:20.976 A:middle
with a project kickoff meeting.

00:11:21.016 --> 00:11:22.826 A:middle
[Laughter]

00:11:22.826 --> 00:11:25.956 A:middle
And then headed immediately
into a team building off site.

00:11:26.281 --> 00:11:28.281 A:middle
[Laughter]

00:11:28.546 --> 00:11:30.986 A:middle
Now, of course they are in their
traditional Apple Marketing

00:11:31.066 --> 00:11:32.656 A:middle
Free-Bottom Fridays attire.

00:11:33.456 --> 00:11:35.446 A:middle
They say it's all
part of their process.

00:11:35.446 --> 00:11:36.966 A:middle
I am not sure I get it.

00:11:37.536 --> 00:11:40.956 A:middle
Ultimately, this
didn't yield any names,

00:11:40.956 --> 00:11:42.976 A:middle
so they called in a consultant.

00:11:43.036 --> 00:11:45.036 A:middle
[Laughter]

00:11:45.056 --> 00:11:49.426 A:middle
He told them the answer
was to be found within.

00:11:49.426 --> 00:11:53.056 A:middle
Not within themselves,
but within Yosemite.

00:11:53.416 --> 00:11:58.456 A:middle
And so the new name for
OS X is OS X El Capitan.

00:11:59.516 --> 00:12:08.116 A:middle
[Applause]

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

