00:26:54.676 --> 00:26:55.096 A:middle
to the Mac.

00:26:55.596 --> 00:26:58.826 A:middle
And pro app makers are seeing
the benefits of Metal as well,

00:26:59.096 --> 00:27:01.416 A:middle
people like The Foundry
and Autodesk.

WEBVTT
