intelligence and Siri.

00:29:22.716 --> 00:29:26.296 A:middle
Now, Siri has quietly
become incredibly popular.

00:29:26.296 --> 00:29:29.416 A:middle
It serves over a billion
requests per week.

00:29:29.766 --> 00:29:32.466 A:middle
And this is in part because
Siri has gotten so great

00:29:32.466 --> 00:29:33.646 A:middle
at understanding
what we are saying.

00:29:33.646 --> 00:29:36.866 A:middle
In just the last year, we've
seen a 40 percent reduction

00:29:37.456 --> 00:29:41.036 A:middle
in word error rate,
down to 5 percent.

00:29:41.186 --> 00:29:43.236 A:middle
That's an industry
leading number.

00:29:43.676 --> 00:29:45.946 A:middle
And Siri is 40 percent
faster than ever

00:29:45.946 --> 00:29:48.356 A:middle
at responding to what we say.

00:29:49.096 --> 00:29:53.416 A:middle
Now, for iOS 9, Siri has a
beautiful new UI and is capable

00:29:53.416 --> 00:29:54.526 A:middle
of doing so much more.

00:29:55.466 --> 00:29:57.106 A:middle
Things like "show me photos

00:29:57.106 --> 00:30:01.626 A:middle
from Utah last August" can
instantly show you the right

WEBVTT
