with formatting options,
so it's easy, for instance,

00:46:28.016 --> 00:46:31.206 A:middle
to create titles, heading
styles, numbered lists.

00:46:31.916 --> 00:46:35.406 A:middle
But of course, we all like to
create checklists in our notes,

00:46:35.406 --> 00:46:37.176 A:middle
and so Notes makes
that really easy.

00:46:37.506 --> 00:46:39.836 A:middle
And of course, you can
just check off your items

00:46:40.146 --> 00:46:40.726 A:middle
with just a tap.

00:46:41.886 --> 00:46:44.146 A:middle
