01:19:04.496 --> 01:19:07.096 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Apps plus handheld devices,

01:19:07.096 --> 01:19:11.156 A:middle
I think that's a watershed
moment in civilization.

01:19:11.156 --> 01:19:12.656 A:middle
I put it up there
with the invention

01:19:12.656 --> 01:19:14.506 A:middle
of the microscope
and the telescope.

01:19:14.506 --> 01:19:21.876 A:middle
We live in a time where the most
powerful tools ever imagined

01:19:21.876 --> 01:19:25.866 A:middle
to investigate and probe
our world are in the hand

01:19:25.866 --> 01:19:26.926 A:middle
of essentially everyone.

01:19:29.146 --> 01:19:32.116 A:middle
&gt;&gt; If you think the Industrial
Revolution was transformational,

01:19:32.116 --> 01:19:34.126 A:middle
the App Store is way bigger.

01:19:34.156 --> 01:19:37.396 A:middle
I don't think we've seen
anything reach a mass adoption

01:19:37.396 --> 01:19:38.736 A:middle
at anything close to this pace.

01:19:38.826 --> 01:19:42.656 A:middle
It took, for example,
electricity over a hundred years

01:19:42.656 --> 01:19:44.776 A:middle
to get to its first
50 million users.

01:19:45.046 --> 01:19:48.486 A:middle
It took television 13
years, and the App Store got

01:19:48.536 --> 01:19:49.976 A:middle
to 50 million users
in only 17 months.

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

01:20:02.156 --> 01:20:04.406 A:middle
&gt;&gt; The thing the App
Store did was give each

01:20:04.556 --> 01:20:06.166 A:middle
and every developer a voice.

01:20:06.166 --> 01:20:09.776 A:middle
It's a testament that two
guys in a room working

01:20:09.816 --> 01:20:13.226 A:middle
on an idea can launch an app
and instantly have hundreds

01:20:13.226 --> 01:20:14.756 A:middle
of millions of people
very quickly.

01:20:14.756 --> 01:20:19.396 A:middle
The iPhone made photography
universally accessible.

01:20:26.046 --> 01:20:29.206 A:middle
&gt;&gt; I cannot think
of a single industry

01:20:29.206 --> 01:20:31.196 A:middle
that doesn't need an app.

01:20:31.196 --> 01:20:33.256 A:middle
People want data at
their fingertips.

01:20:33.256 --> 01:20:35.216 A:middle
They want personalized
experiences.

01:20:35.506 --> 01:20:38.836 A:middle
They want power over
their money.

01:20:38.836 --> 01:20:42.406 A:middle
And it's not just for banking;
it's for every industry.

01:20:42.406 --> 01:20:45.146 A:middle
The App Store has fundamentally
shifted how we all need

01:20:45.146 --> 01:20:45.656 A:middle
to deliver.

01:20:45.656 --> 01:20:47.976 A:middle
It's leveling the playing field.

01:20:52.046 --> 01:20:54.736 A:middle
&gt;&gt; We don't have to own things.

01:20:54.736 --> 01:20:57.046 A:middle
We don't have to
own our own cars.

01:20:57.046 --> 01:20:59.126 A:middle
We don't have to
own our own music.

01:20:59.126 --> 01:21:02.836 A:middle
We can call it up
when we need it.

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

01:20:59.126 --> 01:21:02.836 A:middle
We can call it up
when we need it.

01:21:02.836 --> 01:21:05.106 A:middle
That's a big change, all
flowing from the idea

01:21:05.106 --> 01:21:07.776 A:middle
of not just convenience
but people building

01:21:07.876 --> 01:21:10.306 A:middle
up an infrastructure
around that.

01:21:10.306 --> 01:21:13.546 A:middle
We are now talking
not about hundreds

01:21:13.546 --> 01:21:16.756 A:middle
of people getting the benefits
of an idea, but millions.

01:21:22.846 --> 01:21:25.226 A:middle
&gt;&gt; If you had told me when I
was a kid that you would be able

01:21:25.346 --> 01:21:30.136 A:middle
to write an idea and then film
that idea and then distribute it

01:21:30.136 --> 01:21:32.306 A:middle
to the world on a device
that you could also put

01:21:32.306 --> 01:21:35.256 A:middle
in your pocket, I would
never have stopped laughing,

01:21:35.676 --> 01:21:36.626 A:middle
and I would have
thought you were insane.

01:21:38.446 --> 01:21:40.526 A:middle
The App Store gives
everyone access

01:21:40.706 --> 01:21:43.116 A:middle
to incredibly powerful tools,

01:21:44.656 --> 01:21:47.766 A:middle
and there's an incredible
generation of filmmakers

01:21:47.766 --> 01:21:48.606 A:middle
and storytellers to come.

01:21:59.096 --> 01:22:02.646 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Kids love technology,
and they love interacting

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

01:21:59.096 --> 01:22:02.646 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Kids love technology,
and they love interacting

01:22:02.816 --> 01:22:06.456 A:middle
with the iPad and with apps.

01:22:06.456 --> 01:22:10.216 A:middle
That wonder and awe that gets
ignited is actually being

01:22:10.406 --> 01:22:13.596 A:middle
utilized to help
that person learn.

01:22:13.596 --> 01:22:15.796 A:middle
Certainly in education
there's so much potential

01:22:15.986 --> 01:22:18.256 A:middle
to take the classroom
with you anywhere.

01:22:23.046 --> 01:22:25.846 A:middle
&gt;&gt; We all know we are
in this magic moment.

01:22:26.326 --> 01:22:30.716 A:middle
There are so many incredible
apps, and they do things

01:22:30.716 --> 01:22:32.976 A:middle
for people that change
their lives.

01:22:35.586 --> 01:22:37.646 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Music for me,
it's like everything.

01:22:37.766 --> 01:22:39.026 A:middle
It's really special.

01:22:39.026 --> 01:22:46.576 A:middle
This amazing feeling that
music gives me, I want everyone

01:22:46.686 --> 01:22:50.796 A:middle
to have that, even if
the person cannot hear.

01:22:50.796 --> 01:22:57.856 A:middle
So the idea of the app is to
introduce music for deaf people.

01:22:57.856 --> 01:23:03.546 A:middle
I am going to put these on
your wrist, so if you play,

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

01:22:57.856 --> 01:23:03.546 A:middle
I am going to put these on
your wrist, so if you play,

01:23:03.546 --> 01:23:06.856 A:middle
you can feel the vibrations.

01:23:09.066 --> 01:23:09.886 A:middle
&gt;&gt; I can feel it.

01:23:10.046 --> 01:23:11.976 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Did you feel that, Rob?

01:23:16.116 --> 01:23:21.786 A:middle
My dream is to bring
music to everyone.

01:23:27.106 --> 01:23:30.276 A:middle
&gt;&gt; It is an amazing
time to be a developer.

01:23:30.276 --> 01:23:32.986 A:middle
We are still just at the
beginning of all this,

01:23:32.986 --> 01:23:37.096 A:middle
this moment where the technology
of an iPhone and an iPad

01:23:37.096 --> 01:23:40.876 A:middle
and the Watch enable so
many incredible things.

01:23:44.426 --> 01:23:47.106 A:middle
There's so much that can
still change and evolve due

01:23:47.106 --> 01:23:48.976 A:middle
to the power of applications.

01:23:49.516 --> 01:24:19.516 A:middle
[Music]

WEBVTT
