01:24:37.236 --> 01:24:38.796 A:middle
for everything that you've done.

01:24:38.946 --> 01:24:39.416 A:middle
Thank you.

01:24:40.516 --> 01:24:43.176 A:middle
[Applause]

01:24:43.676 --> 01:24:47.486 A:middle
