so you will get really
high-fidelity calls right

01:31:47.526 --> 01:31:47.976 A:middle
on your wrist.

01:31:48.516 --> 01:31:52.816 A:middle
[Applause]

01:31:53.316 --> 01:31:54.376 A:middle
And with Health &amp; Fitness,

01:31:54.886 --> 01:31:57.366 A:middle
already Apple Watch is a great
partner for Health &amp; Fitness.

01:31:57.806 --> 01:32:01.206 A:middle
With watchOS 2, we are enabling
your favorite fitness apps

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

01:31:57.806 --> 01:32:01.206 A:middle
With watchOS 2, we are enabling
your favorite fitness apps

01:32:01.206 --> 01:32:02.816 A:middle
to run natively on the Watch

01:32:02.816 --> 01:32:05.836 A:middle
so you can use them wherever
you are, and your workouts

01:32:05.836 --> 01:32:07.936 A:middle
with these apps will
contribute directly

01:32:07.936 --> 01:32:10.306 A:middle
to your all-day activity,
which will be really great,

01:32:10.306 --> 01:32:11.656 A:middle
so if you go on a bike
ride, it will count.

01:32:12.516 --> 01:32:14.926 A:middle
[Applause]

01:32:15.426 --> 01:32:17.876 A:middle
We are also enabling
Siri to start workouts,

01:32:17.876 --> 01:32:20.076 A:middle
so you can just raise your
wrist and say, hey, Siri,

01:32:20.076 --> 01:32:21.466 A:middle
start a 30-minute
run in the park,

01:32:21.466 --> 01:32:24.076 A:middle
and it will start the Workout
app and get it going for you.

01:32:24.536 --> 01:32:27.866 A:middle
You can also say things like
"go for a 300-calorie bike ride"

01:32:28.146 --> 01:32:31.436 A:middle
or "go for a 5-mile run, "
and it will start the workout

01:32:31.436 --> 01:32:32.976 A:middle
for you without having to
touch the watch at all.

01:32:33.496 --> 01:32:35.036 A:middle
When you achieve something,

01:32:35.036 --> 01:32:37.296 A:middle
there are some beautiful new
achievements you will see

01:32:37.646 --> 01:32:38.526 A:middle
that look like this.

01:32:39.116 --> 01:32:40.886 A:middle
They spin right in, they're
beautiful, you can play

01:32:40.886 --> 01:32:42.746 A:middle
with them in 3D on the
Watch, they are engraved

01:32:42.746 --> 01:32:45.896 A:middle
on the back now with your
name, and you can share these

01:32:45.896 --> 01:32:48.756 A:middle
with people over Messages,
Facebook, or Twitter.

01:32:48.996 --> 01:32:52.376 A:middle
Really cool Health &amp; Fitness.

01:32:53.516 --> 01:32:56.356 A:middle
[Applause]

01:32:56.856 --> 01:32:58.366 A:middle
With Apple Pay, you saw some

01:32:58.366 --> 01:33:00.066 A:middle
of the great new
support we are bringing

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

01:32:58.366 --> 01:33:00.066 A:middle
of the great new
support we are bringing

01:33:00.066 --> 01:33:01.536 A:middle
for store cards and
rewards cards.

01:33:01.536 --> 01:33:03.126 A:middle
We are supporting
that in the Watch,

01:33:03.126 --> 01:33:05.726 A:middle
so you can select a store card
and use it right in your Watch

01:33:05.726 --> 01:33:07.836 A:middle
in a merchant terminal
just by waving it

01:33:07.836 --> 01:33:08.986 A:middle
at the store stand there.

01:33:08.986 --> 01:33:11.686 A:middle
And with Wallet coming to Watch,

01:33:11.836 --> 01:33:13.596 A:middle
all of your rewards cards
will be right there,

01:33:13.596 --> 01:33:15.546 A:middle
and you can also use those
right from your Watch

01:33:15.546 --> 01:33:16.446 A:middle
as you are doing purchases.

01:33:17.396 --> 01:33:19.696 A:middle
With Transit, we are
supporting, of course,

