Let's go through
some of the things

01:35:42.816 --> 01:35:44.996 A:middle
that will be possible
now in watchOS 2.

01:35:44.996 --> 01:35:45.846 A:middle
You can see how we did on this.

01:35:46.386 --> 01:35:48.806 A:middle
So one of the things we
heard was really wanted

01:35:48.806 --> 01:35:50.816 A:middle
to access the microphone
on the Watch.

01:35:51.346 --> 01:35:54.146 A:middle
So yes, in watchOS 2, you can
access the microphone right

01:35:54.146 --> 01:35:56.546 A:middle
on the Watch and bring that
audio right into your app.

01:35:57.516 --> 01:36:00.046 A:middle
[Applause]

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

01:35:57.516 --> 01:36:00.046 A:middle
[Applause]

